item.title: CVE-2023-29069|2023-11-22T06:26:45.699Z -- autodesk -- desktop%20connector
item.description: A maliciously crafted DLL file can be forced to install onto a non-default location, and attacker can overwrite parts of the product with malicious DLLs. These files may then have elevated privileges leading to a Privilege Escalation vulnerability.
